title: The Key
author: The Key
content: The modern world and NFT opportunities open doors to previously inaccessible worlds. For example, who would have thought that Chimera Meta YuG is a project of The Key Games that allows you to make money on the game. - you earn when you just pass the levels - you will earn even more if you invite friends to the game - and the most profitable combo is to play, invite friends and play with themThe official launch of the game has happened today - join the telegram channel https://t.me/+D0mZ6GSk_RE2ZmRiwhere the link will be posted and test the game!
